'''2018年孟加拉國總統選舉'''於2018年2月18日舉行，為一次換屆總統選舉。上一屆任期在2018年4月23日結束。<ref name="PE">{{Cite news |language=en |url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/2018/01/25/presidential-election-february-18/ |title=Presidential Election February 18 |work=Dhaka Tribune |access-date= |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929183142/https://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/2018/01/25/presidential-election-february-18/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年1月25日，{{link-en|孟加拉國選舉委員會|Bangladesh Election Commission}}公佈選舉日期<ref name="ECG">{{citation|title=Gazette of Election Announcement|language=bn|url=http://www.ecs.gov.bd/files/Ti2KcaH2ZP30hncZTOiTVzPLtsh29ReIGBjIKJcU.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427094555/http://www.ecs.gov.bd/files/Ti2KcaH2ZP30hncZTOiTVzPLtsh29ReIGBjIKJcU.pdf|dead-url=yes|archivedate=2018-04-27|accessdate=2020-08-22}}</ref>，當任總統[[阿卜杜勒·哈米德_(政治人物)|阿卜杜勒·哈米德]]再次受到提名成為執政黨候選人<ref name="HNP">{{Cite news|language=en|url=https://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/politics/2018/02/01/pm-hasina-calls-president-hamid/|title=Handing the nomination paper|work=Dhaka Tribune|access-date=|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929185949/https://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/politics/2018/02/01/pm-hasina-calls-president-hamid/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由於沒有其他候選人，選舉委員會宣佈哈米德成為新任總統，並在同年4月24日宣誓就職，成為該國歷史上第一名連任的總統<ref name="UR">{{Cite news |url=https://www.thedailystar.net/politics/president-abdul-hamid-made-unique-record-in-the-history-of-bangladesh-by-swearing-1567549 |title=Unique record by Hamid |language=en |work=The Daily Star |access-date= |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930015019/https://www.thedailystar.net/politics/president-abdul-hamid-made-unique-record-in-the-history-of-bangladesh-by-swearing-1567549 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SH">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bssnews.net/newsDetails.php?cat=0&id=738569&date=2018-04-23|title=Swearing-in ceremony of Hamid|work=BSS News|access-date=|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427184505/http://www.bssnews.net/newsDetails.php?cat=0&id=738569&date=2018-04-23|archive-date=2018-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

